    <body>
        <section name="yeti-maven-plugin">
            <p>The yeti-maven-plugin is used for compiling/running yeti code in maven. </p>
            <p>If there are problems please let us know.</p>
        </section>
        <section name="Requirements">
            <ul>
                <li>Maven 2.0.7</li>
                <li>JDK 1.5</li>
                <li><bold>No need to install <a href="http://mth.github.com/yeti/">yeti</a> !</bold></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
       <p>Thanks to team from the <a href="http://scala-tools.org/mvnsites/maven-scala-plugin/index.html">maven-scala-plugin</a>.
       This plugin is based on code from them.</p>
    </body>
